      "author": "DFCEO",
      "description": "## STP Viewer v0.1.0\n\nFirst release of the Obsidian STP Viewer plugin.\n\n### Features\n- 3D STEP file preview with OpenCascade WASM + Three.js\n- Orbit controls (rotate/zoom/pan)\n- View presets: ISO, Front, Right, Top\n- Display modes: Solid, Wireframe\n- Shaded-with-edges mode\n- 1:1 actual size display\n- Dynamic scale bar\n- XYZ coordinate axis with labels\n- Auto-adaptive grid plane\n- Dark theme support\n- Supports .stp and .step files",
